- `APIDataNode` as the read-side concept when relevant to DataNode consumers

It should not own:

- SimpleTable behavior
- FastAPI architecture
- workspace payloads
- orchestration/release workflows
- RBAC
- portfolio construction

Out-of-scope routing:

- SimpleTable work -> `docs/astro/data_publishing/simple_tables/SKILL.md`
